1. *Rekoh* da ću se vratiti kasnije. (I said I would come back later.)
2. *Rekoh* joj da je volim. (I told her that I love her.)
3. Ona mi *rekla* da je to dovoljno. (She told me that it was enough.)
4. *Rekoh* im da mogu da pomognem. (I told them that I could help.)
5. Oni su *rekli* da će doći sutra. (They said that they would come tomorrow.)
6. *Rekla* sam da se trudim da ne budem nervozna. (I said I was trying not to be nervous.)